text: Anna Dlasková (born 6 October 1995) is a Czech football Defender, currently playing for Sparta Praha in the Czech First Division.Profile at Sparta websiteProfile at UEFA website She is a member of the Czech national team. Dlasková made her debut for the national team in a match against Poland on 22 June 2013. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Czech women's footballers Category:Czech Republic women's international footballers Category:People from Mladá Boleslav Category:Women's association football defenders Category:AC Sparta Praha (women) players Category:Czech First Division (women) players
